{"tid":377591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日將自己地位睇得好重要","createTime":"2017-08-27T19:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T17:39:42.000Z","uid":33746,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"900e88a8fb8847f77dee73497e0dfee82f8cde2b","tid":377591,"uid":33746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:53:21.000Z","msg":"喺社交生活上經常都覺得自己佔有一個地位。<br />\n可能同性格有關，鍾意講下笑，得閒又挖苦下人一句。<br />\n其實咁做都係想其他人記得我嘅存在，唔想俾人忽視。<br />\n可能其他人已經將我定位做一個小丑，但我都唔介意。<br />\n應該係話無得我介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n當我以為可以融入依個圈子時，就被拒諸門外。<br />\n我問自己點解？<br />\n人地無當過你係一份子，心諗小丑表演完就快啲走啦。<br />\n<br />\n「真是荒謬，把自己看得那麼高。」<br />\n<br />\nFF完腦海就會浮現依句說話，去令自己無咁sad。<br />\n<br />\n每次有類似情況，以上嘅想法都會出現一次，跟住鬧自己一句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戇鳩！</span><br />\n<br />\n然後聽朝繼續返工&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n人生閱歷過淺，思想太幼稚。<br />\n幾時先可以成熟啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"457cc3e89cd819a4210f89f1d42a978c3e481ecf","tid":377591,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:54:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60a3284c42737aa8f36c373f3e8b1e2c2ac3e42c","tid":377591,"uid":137766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T20:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93ab9516bcab71173d17bceddfe2e69414bba97","tid":377591,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T20:35:48.000Z","msg":"你label自己係小丑就知你根本自卑而唔係睇得自己重要<br />\n患難見真情<br />\n係咪fd真係睇有事嗰陣邊個來幫你<br />\n人仔嘅嘢離離合合好常見<br />\n習慣下<br />\n未必真係關你唔受歡迎事"},{"pid":"ddde8348d739b00b071e9f5ff69ff6c03fc201eb","tid":377591,"uid":1367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T21:33:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲人最煩膠又冇料又窮"},{"pid":"2182bcac63fc8a87cdddb53a79177bae0ceeff8a","tid":377591,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T23:43:34.000Z","msg":"好垃圾"},{"pid":"7615bae1e394509bcfd085126982c7adf1a902df","tid":377591,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:07:46.000Z","msg":"社會好現實<br />\n你冇野值得比人痴就冇人會主動痴你<br />\n唔明就趁早收皮啦"},{"pid":"f5ebb35fd5f449db58a52f7a30b2a3d91bd45ce6","tid":377591,"uid":33746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}